<hr />

<h3>3. Date Mask</h3>
<p>A date mask with <code>MaskType="MaskType.Date"</code> for date-specific validation.</p>

<div data-audit-control="MaskedEditExtender-3">
    <label for="txtDate">Date (MM/DD/YYYY):</label>
    <input type="text" id="txtDate" class="form-control" style="max-width: 200px;" placeholder="__/__/____" />
    <MaskedEditExtender TargetControlID="txtDate"
                        Mask="99/99/9999"
                        MaskType="MaskType.Date"
                        PromptCharacter="_"
                        ClearMaskOnLostFocus="true"
                        ClearTextOnInvalid="true" />
</div>

<pre><code>&lt;MaskedEditExtender TargetControlID="txtDate"
                    Mask="99/99/9999"
                    MaskType="MaskType.Date"
                    ClearTextOnInvalid="true" /&gt;</code></pre>

<hr />

