<h3>5. Custom Alphanumeric Mask</h3>
<p>A product code mask mixing letters and digits: <code>AA-9999-LL</code> (A=alphanumeric, L=letter).</p>

<div data-audit-control="MaskedEditExtender-5">
    <label for="txtProduct">Product Code (e.g., A1-2345-XY):</label>
    <input type="text" id="txtProduct" class="form-control" style="max-width: 220px;" placeholder="__-____-__" />
    <MaskedEditExtender TargetControlID="txtProduct"
                        Mask="AA-9999-LL"
                        MaskType="MaskType.None"
                        PromptCharacter="_"
                        ClearMaskOnLostFocus="false" />
</div>

<pre><code>&lt;MaskedEditExtender TargetControlID="txtProduct"
                    Mask="AA-9999-LL"
                    MaskType="MaskType.None"
                    ClearMaskOnLostFocus="false" /&gt;</code></pre>

